agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會轉唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n一開始做sup仔係學至多野，你明晒地盤野知道實際點做，之後先做顧問以後啲人一定勁鐘意你，<br />\n<br />\n一開始乜都唔識做顧問我好憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685df1d6482fd01a3a162126bf06639ed98a207d","tid":221841,"uid":99780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下4年有冇3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n發夢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁4年有冇2萬5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d5b9594180f136ff852d98b96e26bea78f09eb34","tid":221841,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下4年有冇3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n發夢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁4年有冇2萬5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc274db04a332219d5664060c5ccbb78b25c988","tid":221841,"uid":91045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T11:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下4年有冇3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n發夢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁4年有冇2萬5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n做consultant學咩人講人工，ot la快d<br />\ncontractor grad e講緊23k,  <br />\nconsultant 16-18k,  一年加500人工"},{"pid":"86b961985abe87882957e9ed44669d6daca9b431","tid":221841,"uid":99780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下4年有冇3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /