間教你野,完全學壞師<br />\n但係consultant一開波己經頭幾年要接觸畫圖,諗design,出spec,計數加批野<br />\n有機會點觸多些大人物,建立到人際網絡,英文又會有進步<br />\n而大家都係三四年升到e先開始出黎夾圖開會,就咁睇點都係consultant有優勢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但consultant 唔落地盤,連實物都未見過,真係有幫助?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72bceb22691f19698575b8f180ca8b82c8dacce","tid":221841,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下4年有冇3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n發夢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁4年有冇2萬5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n做consultant學咩人講人工，ot la快d<br />\ncontractor grad e講緊23k,  <br />\nconsultant 16-18k,  一年加500人工</blockquote><br />\n邊間開23k咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f6269ed735eb90235568aaec7fd6b0d7df2bb1","tid":221841,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下4年有冇3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n發夢啦</blockquote><br />\n咁4年有冇2萬5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n做consultant學咩人講人工，ot la快d<br />\ncontractor grad e講緊23k,  <br />\nconsultant 16-18k,  一年加500人工</blockquote><br />\n邊間開23k咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n安樂"},{"pid":"ae62f11a22a5ca33081ec5fdb65994ab1d7ada37","tid":221841,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:37:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做十仔啦<br />\n學野快好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學野快人工加得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學野點都係consultant快好多<br />\nsub仔ae得兩種,一開始只係俾大佬點黎點去畫圖,畫圖加畫圖,正常畫圖仔<br />\n另